00:11:42,385 --> 00:11:46,781
Approximate position,
north 22, west 143.

256
00:11:46,824 --> 00:11:50,262
Ceiling closing in fast.

257
00:11:50,306 --> 00:11:53,265
Coral Island calling Sea Bird.

258
00:11:53,309 --> 00:11:55,703
Coral Island calling Sea Bird.

259
00:11:59,271 --> 00:12:01,665
Coral Island calling Sea Bird.

