Pacific Sea Bird
calling Coral Island.

264
00:12:14,156 --> 00:12:16,536
Pacific Sea Bird
calling Coral Island.

265
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:20,075
The lights are off.

266
00:12:26,383 --> 00:12:27,603
Come on, everybody.

267
